The robot is made using basic, easy to acquire parts.
They are as listed below:

  1. Ultrasonic Sensor x1
  2. SPDUINO (ARDUINO UNO CLONE)
  3. GAIT SHIELD (SERVO SHIELD)
  4. POWER HD 1711MG SERVO MOTOR
  5. POWER HD 1900A SERVO MOTOR x1
  5. Lithium Ion Battery (2 Cell Li-ion)

All the other parts are simply mechanical and wiring whcihc depends on personal preference.
